<div class="u2-root u2-sci">

  <section class="u2-sci-hero" aria-label="The science behind UBurn">
    <div class="u2-sci-hero__inner">
      <span class="u2-section-eyebrow">— the science behind uburn</span>
      <h1>The science behind <em>UBurn.</em></h1>
      <p>UBurn is built around <strong>konjac glucomannan</strong> — the only soluble fiber officially recognized by the European Food Safety Authority for supporting satiety. Five additional plant actives round out the formula. Caffeine-free, 30 calories, plant-based, French heritage.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="u2-sci-how" aria-label="How it works">
    <div class="u2-sci-how__inner">
      <div class="u2-sci-how__head u2-reveal">
        <span class="u2-section-eyebrow">— how it works</span>
        <h2>How UBurn helps you <em>stay calm at four.*</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="u2-sci-how__grid">
        <div class="u2-sci-how__card u2-reveal delay-1">
          <div class="u2-sci-how__num">01</div>
          <h3 class="u2-sci-how__title">You feel</h3>
          <p class="u2-sci-how__desc">The afternoon arrives. Blood sugar dips. Cravings start. Instead of reaching for cookies, you pour one scoop into cold water.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="u2-sci-how__card u2-reveal delay-2">
          <div class="u2-sci-how__num">02</div>
          <h3 class="u2-sci-how__title">Glucomannan absorbs water</h3>
          <p class="u2-sci-how__desc">Konjac glucomannan is a soluble fiber that absorbs water and forms a viscous gel in the stomach — the mechanism EFSA recognized for satiety support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="u2-sci-how__card u2-reveal delay-3">
          <div class="u2-sci-how__num">03</div>
          <h3 class="u2-sci-how__title">You ask for less</h3>
          <p class="u2-sci-how__desc">Satiety is signaled naturally. You make it to dinner without raiding the pantry. No willpower required — just physiology.*</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="u2-sci-pillars" aria-label="Science pillars">
    <div class="u2-sci-pillars__inner">
      <div class="u2-sci-pillars__head u2-reveal">
        <span class="u2-section-eyebrow">— the four pillars</span>
        <h2>What makes UBurn <em>different.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="u2-sci-pillars__grid">
        <article class="u2-sci-pillars__card u2-reveal delay-1">
          <div class="u2-sci-pillars__card-icon">{% render 'u2-icon', name: 'leaf', size: 22 %}</div>
          <h3 class="u2-sci-pillars__card-title">Fills naturally</h3>
          <p class="u2-sci-pillars__card-desc">Konjac glucomannan absorbs ~50× its weight in water. A natural gel forms — no synthetic suppressants.*</p>
        </article>
        <article class="u2-sci-pillars__card u2-reveal delay-2">
          <div class="u2-sci-pillars__card-icon">{% render 'u2-icon', name: 'sparkle', size: 20 %}</div>
          <h3 class="u2-sci-pillars__card-title">Slows sugar release</h3>
          <p class="u2-sci-pillars__card-desc">The gel slows gastric emptying — gentler post-meal blood sugar response as part of a balanced diet.*</p>
        </article>
        <article class="u2-sci-pillars__card u2-reveal delay-3">
          <div class="u2-sci-pillars__card-icon">{% render 'u2-icon', name: 'globe', size: 22 %}</div>
          <h3 class="u2-sci-pillars__card-title">100% plant fiber</h3>
          <p class="u2-sci-pillars__card-desc">Konjac is a perennial plant root from East Asia. Caffeine-free. Vegan. Gluten-free formula.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="u2-sci-pillars__card u2-reveal delay-3">
          <div class="u2-sci-pillars__card-icon">{% render 'u2-icon', name: 'flask', size: 20 %}</div>
          <h3 class="u2-sci-pillars__card-title">Third-party lab tested</h3>
          <p class="u2-sci-pillars__card-desc">Every batch tested for purity, heavy metals, and microbial safety. Crafted with French heritage since 2024.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="u2-sci-efsa" aria-label="EFSA approval detail">
    <div class="u2-sci-efsa__inner">
      <div class="u2-sci-efsa__card u2-reveal">
        <span class="u2-sci-efsa__badge">{% render 'u2-icon', name: 'check', size: 12 %} EFSA-recognized</span>
        <h2>The only fiber with this approval.</h2>
        <p class="u2-sci-efsa__quote">"Konjac glucomannan contributes to the maintenance of normal blood cholesterol levels and to the reduction of body weight in the context of an energy-restricted diet."</p>
        <p>The European Food Safety Authority (EFSA) — Europe's equivalent of an FDA-style scientific review body — recognized konjac glucomannan for satiety support under <strong>EU Regulation 432/2012 · ID 3120</strong>. The recognition requires a specific protocol :</p>
        <ul>
          <li>3 grams per day, divided in 3 servings of 1g each</li>
          <li>Taken with 1–2 large glasses of water</li>
          <li>Before meals</li>
          <li>In the context of an energy-restricted diet</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 18px;">UBurn delivers <strong>3g of glucomannan per scoop</strong>, designed to be consumed once daily with water 30 minutes before your most challenging eating moment (typically 4 PM).</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="u2-sci-disc" aria-label="FDA disclaimer">
    <div class="u2-sci-disc__inner">
      <h3>FDA Disclaimer</h3>
      <p>UBurn is a dietary supplement containing konjac glucomannan. Glucomannan supports satiety as part of a healthy lifestyle.* Recommended use : 3g/day in 3 doses of 1g with 1–2 large glasses of water before meals. Not a substitute for a balanced diet. Not recommended during pregnancy or breastfeeding.</p>
      <p>*These statements have not been evaluated by the FDA. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Individual results may vary.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="u2-sci-cta" aria-label="Start ritual">
    <h2>Ready to start <em>your ritual?</em></h2>
    <p>Cold water. One scoop. 30 seconds. The afternoon you've been hoping for.</p>
    {% render 'u2-cta-primary', text: 'start my pack', link: '/products/ube-poudre?variant=51289200034111', on_dark: true %}
  </section>

</div>

